  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "67-year-old Veda caught with drugs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 67-year-old doctor who ran a commercial dispensary in Anuradhapura city was arrested by the Divisional Crime Investigation Division attached to the Anuradhapura Police along with 2260 mg of heroin.",
        "According to an information received by an officer of the Anuradhapura headquarters police, a police officer signaled with his hand to stop the van in which the doctor was traveling. The van stopped in front of his house after he was chased from behind because the van did not stop.",
        "The police officers who checked the van found a parcel of narcotics. Further, the police officers who checked it stated that the person who pretended to be a doctor is 67 years old and he was registered in 2015."
      ],
